<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_171_r2l26"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als vvir vormals an ewr fürſtlıch gnade braht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>entſage<ex>n</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r2l27"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> als vns die edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / her Reynhart vnd her Johan <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Hanaw </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r2l28">getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daran ein gütlıch ſteen <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn vnd vns ıſt / das nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r2l29">auf ſant <expan>Mert<ex>eins</ex></expan> tag awſgeet / Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>willıge<ex>n</ex></expan> dienſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r2l30">willen etwas <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> gemüwet ſein / vnd den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw / darvmb </ab>
