<ab facs="#facs_171_r2l35">vnd ſtellen <expan>moͦchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wir cʒevörderſt <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
