</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_171" id="85r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Bysch<ex>of</ex></expan> czü Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als wir vormals an ewr fürstlich gnade braht
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>entsage<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als uns die edeln
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, her Reynhart und her Johan,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü Hanaw, getan
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daran ein gütlich steen
                        <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in und uns ist, das nu <app><note><q type="date">auf sant
                            <expan>Mert<ex>eins</ex></expan> tag</q>11.11.1410</note></app> awsgeet. Also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dienst willen etwas
                                <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> gemüwet sein und den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw darumb ewr botschaft tün und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, also daz die
                        sache <add>noch</add> etwielange gütlichen bestellet werde; in
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit sich die ding
                            <add>also</add> schicken und stellen <expan>moͦchte<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir czevörderst <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> genüszen, daz die sache gnediklich abgetragen
                        würde. Und wöllet <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in
                        den und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnediklich <expan>bevolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Als etc. <add>und</add> das <add>umb
                            etc.</add> Und wie das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade bestell, daz
                        lasset uns an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, den wir darauf <expan>warte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geheisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Sy<ex>monis</ex></expan> et Jude. </ab>
</div>
